data.description: Go and SHOW.  Are you tired of paying the electric bills?  Welcome to Landing at Central Park, an eco-friendly haven in Fredericksburg, VA. This home offers a perfect blend of modern living and environmental consciousness. Most distinctly,  the home has SOLAR PANELS that provide sustainable energy solutions and drastically reduce utility costs. The solar panels have been completely PAID OFF, so the owner-only expense for electricity was $84  from December 2023 through March 2024, even during the coldest months of the year.  You will live in style with an open-concept floor plan, stainless steel appliances, ample storage space, and comfortable, bright bedrooms. The property is in a desirable neighborhood with easy access to amenities, shopping centers, city trails, and major transportation routes, making it a true hidden gem.
